88</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"72c47d2319e4d00aa1c95ada6ce8820a76688fbf","tid":1224183,"uid":36744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"繼續有狗做翻人固然係好事，但開始擔心狗隊唔夠人會再請多啲外判..."},{"pid":"8a936fb545721259f4eaf70582fa2c76febb787b","tid":1224183,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要小看網絡平台的威力，<br />\n每多一個發聲，<br />\n就多一份力量！！！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以都叫朋友係自己既網絡平台到發聲<br />\n呢個係其中一個發聲方法<br />\n不要俾政府睇死<br />\n我地係唔會就咁屈服強權</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"29dd3c46f6de98d85437c947650e371893d8446e","tid":1224183,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcf3e33aa6de83675b6f6b8d7e64066651bc6df","tid":1224183,"uid":24853,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"4dd5a61e69bc31f7d5cd557c38bff9ab2dee3e29","tid":1224183,"uid":189012,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"quote":{"pid":"21439254647fedf69bafddc91846a75b81bf8c81","tid":1224183,"uid":22362,"like":667,"dislike":2,"score":665,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:26: